## Range filter

Range filter is a range slider with single or double handles used to filter posts by a [Number field](docs.getvoxel.io_articles_number-field_.md), or [Product field](docs.getvoxel.io_articles_product-field_.md) (price)

## Options

- Label
- Placeholder
- Key
- Data source
- Handles:

1\. Single handle

2\. Double handles
- Range start
- Range end
- Step size
- Comparison:

1\. Inside selected range

2\. Outside selected range
- Format display value
- Prefix
- Suffix
- Description
- Icon

## Display modes

This filter has two display mods when added to your [search form](docs.getvoxel.io_articles_search-form-vx-widget_.md), Popup and Inline, previewed below.

## Default values

This filer expects a number as a default value when Single handle

It expects a Start and End number value when Double handle
